                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Subscription</span>
                <span class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/20 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">Free Tier</span>
